OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783671598
OL,3,CDads say 'ambitious' scheme for
OL,4,Cdedicated basketball facility is
OL,5,C'doable'
OL,7,FMerseyside correspondent Andy Bonner
OL,8,Fwatched a training session with the
OL,9,FWirral Raptors.
OL,11,FTwo dads behind a multi-million pound
OL,12,Fproposal to create a dedicated
OL,13,Fbasketball facility in the sport's
OL,14,Fhistoric UK home say they are
OL,15,Fcommitted to making it happen.
OL,17,FMichael Holt and Richard Stubbs came
OL,18,Fup with the plan after watching their
OL,19,Fchildren play in shared courts in
OL,20,FWirral, Merseyside.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783671598
OL,3,CDads say 'ambitious' scheme for
OL,4,Cdedicated basketball facility is
OL,5,C'doable'
OL,7,FMichael said: "I'm an architect by
OL,8,Ftrade, and Rich is in finance. So we
OL,9,Fput our heads together and thought,
OL,10,Fwe've got to be able to make something
OL,11,Fhappen. And then we realised that
OL,12,Fthere was something to this.
OL,14,F"So we started to do the research,
OL,15,Ffound out that Birkenhead was the
OL,16,Ffirst game of basketball competitively
OL,17,Fin the UK in 1892, and then we decided
OL,18,Fthere was a narrative."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783671598
OL,3,CDads say 'ambitious' scheme for
OL,4,Cdedicated basketball facility is
OL,5,C'doable'
OL,7,FRichard added: "We looked at
OL,8,Fbasketball as the second most played
OL,9,Fsport in the country and thought, well
OL,10,Fsomething doesn't add up.
OL,12,F"The sport has grown exponentially
OL,13,Fover the last few years. More kids
OL,14,Fplay basketball every week than rugby
OL,15,Fand tennis combined, which is
OL,16,Fremarkable.
OL,18,F"But then you look at the difference
OL,19,Fin infrastructure and there's nothing
OL,20,Fthere. So we decided to try and do
OL,21,Fsomething about it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783671598
OL,3,CDads say 'ambitious' scheme for
OL,4,Cdedicated basketball facility is
OL,5,C'doable'
OL,7,FCurrently, some children have to
OL,8,Ftravel for up to an hour to play
OL,9,F"home" matches.
OL,11,FTerry Evans, co-chairman and under-10s
OL,12,Fcoach at Wirral Raptors, said it is
OL,13,Falso problematic using training
OL,14,Ffacilities shared with other sports
OL,15,Faround the borough.
OL,17,FHe said: "You can see on the floor the
OL,18,Fmarkings are really difficult. There
OL,19,Fare three lines on the sidelines.
OL,20,FThat's a real struggle because a lot
OL,21,Fof kids are stepping out.
OL,26,@yD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783671598
OL,3,CDads say 'ambitious' scheme for
OL,4,Cdedicated basketball facility is
OL,5,C'doable'
OL,7,F"To help them understand the game it's
OL,8,Freally quite hard. There's nowhere
OL,9,Freally to put your feet so you can
OL,10,Fstep out of bounds really easily."
OL,12,FUnder the proposals, the brand new
OL,13,Ffacility would include a 3,000-seater
OL,14,Fshow court which they hope would allow
OL,15,Fthe creation of a Wirral-based
OL,16,Fprofessional outfit.
OL,18,FThere would also be two courts to the
OL,19,Fstandards required by FIBA, the
OL,20,Fsport's governing body.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783671598
OL,3,CDads say 'ambitious' scheme for
OL,4,Cdedicated basketball facility is
OL,5,C'doable'
OL,7,FRichard explained, "You have to have a
OL,8,Ftwo meter run off (behind the
OL,9,Fbaskets). Incredibly there are very,
OL,10,Fvery few basketball courts anywhere
OL,11,Fnear here that have that.
OL,13,F"If you're running from one side of
OL,14,Fthe court to the other, it's to stop
OL,15,Fyou running into a wall. It's a safety
OL,16,Fthing."
OL,18,FThe community-led plan also features a
OL,19,Fspecial educational needs school which
OL,20,Fthe men hope will give a unique offer
OL,21,Fwith the co-location of services.
OL,26,@oD@TOUpD@SpmqD@Hpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
