OL,3,CDads say 'ambitious' scheme for
OL,4,Cdedicated basketball facility is
OL,5,C'doable'
OL,7,FBasketball was invented by a YMCA
OL,8,Fteacher in the United States in 1891.
OL,9,FThe following year, it was adopted by
OL,10,Fthe YMCA in Birkenhead.
OL,12,FIn the 1930s, nearby Hoylake YMCA
OL,13,Fbecame the first British champions of
OL,14,Fthe sport.
OL,16,FA local resurgence in the late 1970s
OL,17,Fwas spearheaded by teacher Tony
OL,18,FWhitehead, who inspired a whole
OL,19,Fgeneration of players.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783671598
OL,3,CDads say 'ambitious' scheme for
OL,4,Cdedicated basketball facility is
OL,5,C'doable'
OL,7,FHis son, Chris, represented England as
OL,8,Fa teenager and now coaches at Wirral
OL,9,FRaptors where he is also co-chairman.
OL,11,FHe said his father "had basketball
OL,12,Fbooming" in the area.
OL,14,F"A lot of the coaches who coach here
OL,15,Fat the Raptors come from my dad's
OL,16,Fcoaching. They've carried on his
OL,17,Flegacy.
OL,26,@tD@HO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783671598
OL,3,CDads say 'ambitious' scheme for
OL,4,Cdedicated basketball facility is
OL,5,C'doable'
OL,7,F"That's what we're trying to do,
OL,8,Ftrying to give an opportunity for kids
OL,9,Fto come and enjoy basketball and enjoy
OL,10,Fthemselves and fall in love with the
OL,11,Fgame like we did when we were young."
OL,13,FRichard and Michael, operating as
OL,14,FTriple Double, say they are in "active
OL,15,Fconversations" with authorities to
OL,16,Fsecure a site in Birkenhead and
OL,17,Fbelieve it could be built by the end
OL,18,Fof 2028.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783671598
OL,3,CDads say 'ambitious' scheme for
OL,4,Cdedicated basketball facility is
OL,5,C'doable'
OL,7,FThey expect to find the money for the
OL,8,Fdevelopment from a combination of
OL,9,Fprivate investment and local
OL,10,Fregeneration funds.
OL,12,FFollowing a feasibility study and a
OL,13,Fsurvey of clubs, they claim there is
OL,14,Fenough demand for the facility to open
OL,15,Fat capacity.
OL,17,FTheir children are excited at the
OL,18,Fprospect.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783671598
OL,3,CDads say 'ambitious' scheme for
OL,4,Cdedicated basketball facility is
OL,5,C'doable'
OL,7,FCoen Holt, 10, said. "It's hard to
OL,8,Ffind courts that are accessible for
OL,9,Fdisabled people or wheelchair
OL,10,Fbasketball. I think if they did this
OL,11,Fit could be a quite good thing."
OL,13,FGeorge Stubbs, 9, said, "I'm very
OL,14,Fproud because there's no basketball
OL,15,Fcourts in Wirral that you can go to.
OL,16,FIt's just really good."
OL,18,FWant more on the issues effecting the
OL,19,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,20,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,21,Four region.
OL,26,@xD@WO]
